  <div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
    <a href="/JuliaLopezMP" class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav">Julia Lopez MP</a>
  </h1>

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/JuliaLopezMP">
      <span class="username u-dir" dir="ltr">@<b class="u-linkComplex-target">JuliaLopezMP</b></span>
    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">(ne Dockerill) Conservative MP for Hornchurch &amp; Upminster. Member of International Trade Committee. Please email all queries to julia.lopez.mp@parliament.uk</p>

  </a>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Thanks <a href="/HaveringCollege" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="16348294"><s>@</s><b>HaveringCollege</b></a>, loved meeting these guys and hearing about their paths to the Railway Academy. Training people for critical infrastructure jobs with a real career structure ahead of them. Also great to see your catering and SEN students at work.<a href="https://t.co/RvEWmQ37NH" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/haveringcollege/status/974672557852020736" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/haveringcollege/status/974672557852020736"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/haveringcolleg</span><span class="invisible">e/status/974672557852020736</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">

        <div class="QuoteTweet-authorAndText u-alignTop">
            
  <div class="QuoteTweet-originalAuthor u-cf u-textTruncate stream-item-header account-group js-user-profile-link">

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Christmas preparations well and truly underway at Elm Park <a href="/PostOffice" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="96966644"><s>@</s><b>PostOffice</b></a> Great to meet Mr Mashadis team and regular customer, Reg, whose dad was the last postman in City of London to use horse-drawn post carriage.   <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">I met senior <a href="/metpoliceuk" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="66967746"><s>@</s><b>metpoliceuk</b></a> officers this morning to discuss Operation Sceptre progress in tackling knife crime, as well as scooter crime &amp; acid attacks. Stayed back to ask questions about triborough pilot &amp; new ward officers but am seeing Deputy Borough Commander tmw to talk more.</p>

We're making sure our young people have the skills they need to get on in life, building an education system fit for the future.<a href="https://t.co/2i0MXRy22D" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/2i0MXRy22D</a></p>

  </ul>

A complex area which raises potential challenges for EU's FTAs as well as UK's <a href="/CommonsIntTrade" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="787957858512044032"><s>@</s><b>CommonsIntTrade</b></a><a href="https://t.co/zcqOYumpiW" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/zcqOYumpiW</a></p>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

  </div>
